---
title: Rich Italian Beef & Leek Penne with Grated Parmesan
description: You can add just about anything to a pasta, but sometimes, simple really is best. Beef mince, leek and celery are cooked down and tossed through twirls of fusilli with a creamy, tomato-based sauce. A little Parmesan on top is all you need to complete this warm and comforting meal.

*We’ve replaced the fusilli in this recipe with penne due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your
recipe card!*
